<h1>Retry (Stable)</h1>
<p>Exponential backoff with jitter. Idempotent by default for read/chat requests.</p>
<pre><code>client.chat({
  model: 'gpt-4o',
  messages,
  policy: {
    retry: { attempts: 3, baseDelayMs: 200, maxDelayMs: 2000 }
  }
});
</code></pre>
<p>Errors classified: network, 5xx, rate-limit w/ retry-after. Tool side effects should be guarded with idempotency keys.</p>
